{"tid":1550683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底防撚完未 肯反擊未 肯醒覺未啊？！","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T23:25:36.000Z","uid":19482,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4ad4ded4755287609bc9ab8a3923d32d9f1231","tid":1550683,"uid":19482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"打撚左三個月既仗 應該係話由雨傘開始打落黎既仗 就係淨係識得防禦 無論陣地戰set roadblock又好 比狗用警棍打又好 都係淨係識防守 你地咁樣係唔會令佢地驚架！只會令佢地更加放心打柒你地 捉曬你地 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醒下啦香港人！我地已經失去左好多手足 係時候反擊啦！</span> 既然防又係比狗拉 反擊又係比狗拉 反擊起碼都有一線生機啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攻守兼備 因時制宜</span></span>"},{"pid":"33e939c595ed444ab5bb7d0b3a9f291361321130","tid":1550683,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=9ec5b387\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"e83576e721412687fab8edbb43518f2efdc58f9a","tid":1550683,"uid":19482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bf52b2cbb38e60992f3eb4393bc717ecc5b0f0d","tid":1550683,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6680245f2b6a890d1cc405159f2ef1ae68f61cdd","tid":1550683,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cbba54e897fdb912e4955c556345b13a105bf90","tid":1550683,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"咁點攻呀。人地咁撚重裝"},{"pid":"f98199a4d35768c1abca31894bded44fc3a2c4e2","tid":1550683,"uid":19482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要一個人反擊 其他人都會有勇氣跟住你反擊 永遠唔好怕做第一個 因為係你後面仲有千千萬萬個兄弟傍住你</span>"},{"pid":"12ccbea43cd2e300ee05070d586df381c73a5393","tid":1550683,"uid":8605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:09:10.000Z","msg":"一大批防暴速龍要避，一小隊藍衫狗真係要主動打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cceaf6b3626294e2240d7822e02107be1a38aa","tid":1550683,"uid":209614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1706b4c0d2a9fd30120fb6e187308b303ac6108","tid":1550683,"uid":1565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"咪撚推人出去送頭啦 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6447ccc1331ae9d14c936705df51489cfa017fd5","tid":1550683,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"攻就平日la<br />\n示威日人地上哂gear 攻條毛咩"},{"pid":"27bdf8d9ff725ba71e712248e5293ff785cb9d09","tid":1550683,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"你諗住還拖 點知有左膠阻住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係後面走曬 得你一個落單 <br />\n唉 灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地做埋我個份"},{"pid":"819879a428fcc2907c4b50cc198d0edd69fc1a6d","tid":1550683,"uid":19482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cbba54e897fdb912e4955c556345b13a105bf90","tid":155